GxfYzifrrl5Q&oe=6A0B449C", "manifest_stream_number": 0, "is_dash_periods": true, "protocol": "https", "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 770.87, "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 1006852, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-722686467569620v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by artificialintelligenceee", "description": "Yes, that life exists…", "duration": 10.449, "timestamp": 1777811801, "uploader_id": "66294766434", "uploader": "Artificial Intelligence (AI)", "channel": "artificialintelligenceee", "like_count": 58739, "comment_count": 583, "comments": [{"author": "kharlifries", "author_id": "60783004514", "id": "18074005355278055", "text": "I used to be Maverick, now I’m the kid. I’d rather be happy, enjoy my life and my people. Earn  an honest living, love my family and focus on what I can control. Because I can’t control any of the things listed in the video. Most of us can’t.", "timestamp": 1778732877}, {"author": "__mohdrehan___", "author_id": "55245513720", "id": "18108235862308874", "text": "🙌🙌🙌", "timestamp": 1778732109}, {"author": "alexander_adam_123", "author_id": "75764501821", "id": "18143921521507123", "text": "But I love the digital life instead of real life", "timestamp": 1778731119}, {"author": "alexander_adam_123", "author_id": "75764501821", "id": "18403815034197898", "text": "Real😢", "timestamp": 1778731081}, {"author": "iam.piiiiyuxh", "author_id": "52756182984", "id": "17929123323273760", "text": "\"Knowledge is a curse\"", "timestamp": 1778727719}, {"author": "gurdyalssingh", "author_id": "49944728004", "id": "18039456572792772", "text": "Ignorance is dangerous, the more you know the more you become humble is real greatness.", "timestamp": 1778709732}, {"author": "barrosfonseca.eduardo", "author_id": "65322890923", "id": "17911438788200567", "text": "😢😢😢😢", "timestamp": 1778707798}, {"author": "okanhasanovv", "author_id": "25883172964", "id": "17926903374289536", "text": "Take me back to 2016…", "timestamp": 1778664024}, {"author": "thcnig", "author_id": "76413965762", "id": "18079737422393203", "text": "Knowledge is a sin. A burden you never asked for. Enlightenment is not for everyone.", "timestamp": 1778650442}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://instagram.fkul19-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.71878-15/686187386_2023125944937370_2848971143640124505_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDAuc2RyLnZpZGVvX2RlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=instagram.fkul19-2.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=110&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHVXD2LNsqNxxxe-AQLrxmUVt_E4lsUFqjGYaZMCsQv3i3UejPHpNix5iIFKCDPO2k&_nc_ohc=ZKtsNr68tosQ7kNvwHKhaEV&_nc_gid=Dnz4CQUdGldOZOPV08CdhQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af6c-IThhTL3KTLWMiwxJgfcDpFa1syvePIGS14Ul9rvIQ&oe=6A0B2BC4&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://instagram.fkul19-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.71878-15/686187386_2023125944937370_2848971143640124505_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDAuc2RyLnZpZGVvX2RlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=instagram.fkul19-2.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=110&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHVXD2LNsqNxxxe-AQLrxmUVt_E4lsUFqjGYaZMCsQv3i3UejPHpNix5iIFKCDPO2k&_nc_ohc=ZKtsNr68tosQ7kNvwHKhaEV&_nc_gid=Dnz4CQUdGldOZOPV08CdhQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af6c-IThhTL3KTLWMiwxJgfcDpFa1syvePIGS14Ul9rvIQ&oe=6A0B2BC4&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1331, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1331"}, {"url": "https://instagram.fkul19-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.71878-15/686187386_2023125944937370_2848971143640124505_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDAuc2RyLnZpZGVvX2RlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbW